---
title: Louisiana Beef & Cheesy Mash Pie with Garlicky Greens
description: Sometimes only a pie will do. Satisfy that craving for something warm, slightly smokey and comforting with this rich, cheesy
mash-topped number. It's Nanna's cooking fused with classic Southern flavours for an explosion of flavour and a dinner that
reminds us why at-home cooking is best.
